{
  "stem": "1917.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, Juppi, you're crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, well, I don't know this woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must have hurt her feelings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said oh, don't worry so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I'm kind of nuts myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said, but I have a certificate to prove it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she said she was so many times in the hospital, she knows that they don't give you too many Coca-Colas in Israel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she-- the said, I thought that you would like some Coke.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a very unique picture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she was very, very close to my sister-- very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm just trying to tell you, she told me, at that time-- she wouldn't let me tape her-- that her colon was connected to her urinary tract by Mengele.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was on the operating table, and she could feel the body of her brother turning cold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She does not remember who liberated her or how she survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She has had a lifelong health problem, as well as emotional problem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She is part of 10 Dutch twins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The other 9 will not come forward.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They cannot deal with any of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She is doing very well today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she's very grateful that we have formed the support group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So from what I can tell you-- that there were some very bizarre experiments.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a very interesting question, because children, or I, as a child, when you are faced with life and death, the only thing that we ever talked about is food, survival, and how to make it from one day to the other.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- I never even learned the name of many of the twins in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
